description.@value: キジル石窟に関する図像学的研究書。本文と計25面の原色版図版からなる。ドイツ隊は石窟に、編号ではなく特徴にもとづく名称をつけており、本書ではそのうち孔雀洞、航海者洞、峡谷洞、洗足洞、財宝洞、マーヤー洞を取り上げる。

An iconography research paper related to the Kizil Caves.  Comprised of the main text and a total of 25 original colors prints.  The German expedition did not number of the grottoes, but named them according to their characteristics. This text describes the peacock cave, navigator’s cave, canyon cave, feet-washing cave, treasure cave and Maya cave.
